'''''Lost in the Feeling''''' is the ninth studio album released by American [[country music]] artist [[Mark Chesnutt]]. The album's first two tracks were both Top 40 singles for songwriter [[Shawn Camp (songwriter)|Shawn Camp]] in 1993.

==Track listing==
