#It Pays Big Money (Camp, Randy Hardison, Wynn Varble) - 4:06
#Love in the Hot Afternoon (Vince Matthews, Keny Westberry) - 3:43
#Angelina (Steve Diamond, Rick Orozco, Vern Dant) - 2:58
